      <odd id="aspace_4c65af2f3fccd52879ea24c8fc19cad1">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 42-C (YRG 42-C), Materials documenting military and wartime experiences of members of the Yale community.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_2dfa136e155fd98bf7ee7b8cf9fdf988">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
